// Improvise = a static ability [CR#702.126a] that functions while the spell
// with improvise is on the stack: "For each generic mana in this spell's total
// cost, you may tap an untapped artifact you control rather than pay that
// mana." Modeled as per-pip ALTERNATIVE PAYMENT (`PayPips`), NOT a cost
// reduction: it "isn't an additional or alternative cost and applies only after
// the total cost ... is determined" ([CR#702.51b]) — the engine reads it only
// in the cost-payment window ([CR#601.2g..601.2h]) and never lowers the mana
// value ([CR#202.3]). The artifact tapped is chosen at payment time
// ([CR#107.5]).
KeywordAbility(
    name: "Improvise",
    template: "improvise",
    abilities: [Static(effects: [
        PayPips(Generic, TapToPay(AllOf([Type(Artifact), ControlledBy(Ref(You))]))),
    ])],
)
